Text: RE MiscI will give you a call tomorrow AM I just got back from Boston so I didnt get your email until now JM Original Message From mailto Sent Monday November AM To Jonathan Mueller Subject Misc Jonathan Hope you had a good Thanksgiving weekend Id like to catch up with you today if possible regarding recruiting etc Can I reach you by phone If so where You can call me toll free at ENRON and follow the menu My extension is X or you can use the voice activated system Thanks Charlie
